TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {73872=Easton Cycling is the leader in composite design, engineering and manufacturing for the bicycle industry. Located in Scotts Valley, California, Easton provides a range of carbon and aluminum wheelsets and components to manufacturers and consumers. Easton products include innovative manufacturing techniques, category-leading performance and consistently great value. Easton wheels and components were ridden to victory at the 2011 Tour de France by Cadel Evans and the BMC Racing Team, who Easton continues to sponsor alongside the world’s best athletes in the road, mountain, track, triathlon and cyclo-cross disciplines.}
